						class="font-semi bold ml-5 text-left text-lg text-[#EDF0FF] md:text-xl lg:ml-10 lg:text-2xl"
					>
						We primarely focus on landing pages. Let us know how we can help
						you! web Development - Mobile friendly - SEO - Creative direction
						and branding - UI / UX Design
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section
		class="mt-0 w-full rounded-xl bg-[url('./mobile-haikei-2.svg')] bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat sm:bg-[url('./mobile-haikei-2.svg')] md:bg-[url('./full-haikei-2.svg')] lg:bg-[url('./full-haikei-2.svg')] lg:bg-cover"
