				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
					Web Development
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-gray-500">
					This is a description of our clients' success stories. They had a
					problem and we provided a solution that improved their online
					presence, saved them time, and boosted their revenue.
				</p>

				<dl
					class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-6 gap-y-10 sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-y-16 lg:gap-x-8"
				>
					<div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
						<dt class="font-medium text-gray-900">Origin</dt>
						<dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
							Designed by Good Goods, Inc.
						</dd>
					</div>
					<div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
						<dt class="font-medium text-gray-900">Material</dt>
						<dd class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
							Solid walnut base with rare earth magnets and powder coated steel
							card cover
						</dd>
					</div>
					<div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
						<dt class="font-medium text-gray-900">Dimensions</dt>
